entries.journal_entry_description: Negal has assisted you in dumping the bodies in the Rryatt Trail. You need to return to Borantok and see if he needs any further assistance in covering up this mess.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Return to Borantok and tell him that no one will ever find the Rodian bodies, and if they do they will assume that the vicious creatures of the Rryatt Trail killed them.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Travel to the cantina in the city of Kachirho and threaten the bartender into not talking.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Before trying anything drastic, Borantok wants you to just try talking to Unluto and see if you can convince Unluto not to turn him in.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Return to Borantok and report your successful conversation with the bartender.
